title: Agito Cosmos 01 - Aqua Viva (2012) (Scanlation) (phillywilly) cb
description:
On one side, the crew of the SS Robin Suzumiya. Enlisted by Captain Sporing for a mission to explore the seabed and collect the remnants of human civilisation, they have laboured at their mission for a long time without knowing its true purpose. Far away on the surface, in his stilt village, young Alfonsino is preparing himself for the trial of cockle-diving. In the depths of the sea, he is drawn to a luminescent stone which will seal his fate... There is also the pretty Agnes, kept alive in a sphere of liquid by a genius without scruples, who Duncan Dimanche is trying to save. They don't know it yet, but the destinies of these heroes are about to cross...

enjoy
